*: {{audio|en-us-abuse-noun.ogg|Audio (US)}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# [[improper|Improper]] [[treatment]] or [[usage]]; application to a wrong or bad [[purpose]]; [[misuse]]; [[perversion]]. {{defdate|from 15th c}}
#* ''Liberty may be endangered by the '''abuses''' of liberty, as well as by the '''abuses''' of power.''- [[w:James Madison|James Madison]]
