From {{etyl|fr}} or {{etyl|fro}} {{term|abuser|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|abusus|abūsus|lang=la}}, perfect active participle of {{term|abutor|abūtor|lang=la}}, from {{term|ab||from, away from|lang=la}} + {{term|utor|ūtor|use|lang=la}}.

====Pronunciation====
